divs: sighting detailsthis is no joke. let me begin to tell you the story. on saturday, june 9th, between 5:30pm and 6:00pm, i was shooting omar on top of the hill at centenial park (dollard des ormeaux, quebec: suburb of montreal). when i got home i began to process my raw pictures and noticed that something was weird between pictures number nor_5676 to nor_5682. at first i thought that it was dust but when i looked closer, it was very clearly a ufo (unidentified flying object). now, i have all the pictures in raw format, so they cannot be touched as so. i also have kept the disk on which i was shooting. these pictures were taken at 1\1000th of a second and as you can see omar in his movement that this object was flying really fast. the whole sequence of shots is no longer than one second. i shot with a nikon d200. you can view the pictures here: www.normedwards.com\3\ufo\page_01.htm
